    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Our Story Section -->
<section class="py-5 bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
        <h2 class="fs-1 fw-bold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
          Chapterless was born from a simple belief: every soul deserves to find the story that speaks to their heart. In a world overflowing with content, we understand the profound loneliness of not knowing where to begin, what to choose, or which story will truly resonate with who you are in this moment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
          We are not just a bookstore. We are curators of human experience, collectors of dreams, and guardians of the stories that have the power to transform lives. Our mission is to bridge the gap between lost souls and the narratives that can guide them home.
        </p>
